<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Hogan Leaves Turner Broadcasting
   To Become a Vice Chairman at Whittle
   ----
   By Peter Waldman
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/18/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
